curam.util.ctm.bom

Interface DeleteBOM

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BusinessObjectModule
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApplicationConfigDeleteBOMImpl, AppResourceDeleteBOMImpl, CodeTableDeleteBOMImpl, CodeTableHierarchyDeleteBOMImpl, CSSAppResourceDeleteBOMImpl, EventDeleteBOMImpl, ImageAppResourceDeleteBOMImpl, PropertiesAppResourceDeleteBOMImpl, PropertiesDeleteBOMImpl, RulesDeleteBOMImpl, SchemaAppResourceDeleteBOMImpl, SectionConfigDeleteBOMImpl, SecurityGroupDeleteBOMImpl, SecurityIdentifierDeleteBOMImpl, SecurityRoleDeleteBOMImpl, TabConfigDeleteBOMImpl, XMLAppResourceDeleteBOMImpl, XSLTemplateDeleteBOMImpl

    public interface DeleteBOM
extends BusinessObjectModule

    Infrastructure depends on BOM implementation for every business object type that can be deleted.

    Infrastructure delegates the responsibility to individual BOM implementation to determine how to delete business object of its kind. Every business object module which needs to be migrated, need to provide its specific implementation.
